Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Spray a shallow baking dish with cooking spray. Mix together the tahini, wheat flour, garlic, egg white, soy sauce, and water in a large bowl. Toss in the tofu, and mix so the tofu is coated. Arrange tofu in prepared baking dish. Bake for 12 to 15 minutes in preheated oven.